Create a Numeric Progression using Inheritance, Polymorphism and the basic concept of C++ and perform the following:

  a. Arithmetic Progression
  b. Geometric Progression
  c. Fibonacci  progression

hint:

  Arithmetic Progression(d)
 a (a+d) (a + 2d) (a +3d)..... 1 2 3    + 1

  Geometric Progression (d)
  a   a*d   (a*d)*d                   1 2 4 8....

  Fibonacci  progression
  0 1 1 2 3 5 8 13     c = a+b

